{"title":"ABAP: Tipos de Dados Locais","uid":"c2c2c2a449602342e5b4349eb0a9a6c0","slug":"curso-abap-basico-03-tipos-locais","date":"2022-11-02T04:15:00.435Z","updated":"2022-11-02T04:18:44.020Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/curso-abap-basico-03-tipos-locais.json","keywords":["SAP","ABAP","Learn","Aprender","Software","Programação","Desenvolvimento","Desenvolvimento de Software"],"cover":"/img/default-cover.png","content":"<p>Os tipos de dados locais representam tipos de dados primitivos <code>predefinidos</code> para utilização em programas ABAP. Esses tipos possuem apenas atributos técnicos, em contraste com os tipos globais.</p>\n<p>Os tipos primitivos podem ser agrupados em:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#principais-tipos-numricos\">Numéricos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#principais-tipos-caracteres\">Caracteres</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tipos-datahora\">Data&#x2F;Hora</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tipos-byte\">Bytes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Principais-Tipos-Numericos\"><a href=\"#Principais-Tipos-Numericos\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Principais Tipos Numéricos\"></a>Principais Tipos Numéricos</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Identificador</th>\n<th>Descrição</th>\n<th>Comprimento</th>\n<th>Limite Negativo</th>\n<th>Limite Positivo</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>Número inteiro de 4 bytes</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>-2147483648</td>\n<td>+2147483647</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>INT8</td>\n<td>Número inteiro de 8 bytes</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>-9223372036854775808</td>\n<td>+9223372036854775807</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DECFLOAT16</td>\n<td>Número com 16 casas decimais</td>\n<td>8 bytes com 16 decimais</td>\n<td>-(1e385 até -1e-383)</td>\n<td>+(+1e-383 até 1e385)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DECFLOAT34</td>\n<td>Número com 34 casas decimais</td>\n<td>16 bytes com 34 decimais</td>\n<td>-(1e6145 até -1e-6143)</td>\n<td>+(+1e-6143 até 1e6145)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_int        <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">i</span>          <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">2147483647</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>       \n    v_int8       <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> int8       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">9223372036854775807</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_decfloat16 <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> decfloat16 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">4611686018427387904</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_decfloat34 <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> decfloat34 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>8948022309329048855892746252172e+<span class=\"token number\">76</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Outros tipos numéricos: <a href=\"https://help.sap.com/doc/abapdocu_751_index_htm/7.51/en-us/abenbuiltin_types_numeric.htm\">B (1-Byte), S (2-Byte), F (Float 8-Byte), P (Packed 1-16 Bytes)</a><br><BR/></p>\n<h3 id=\"Principais-Tipos-Caracteres\"><a href=\"#Principais-Tipos-Caracteres\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Principais Tipos Caracteres\"></a>Principais Tipos Caracteres</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Identificador</th>\n<th>Descrição</th>\n<th>Comprimento</th>\n<th>Detalhes</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>C</td>\n<td>Caracteres</td>\n<td>de 1 (padrão) até 262143</td>\n<td>Comprimento deve ser especificado préviamente (Fixo)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>Caracteres numéricos</td>\n<td>de 1 (padrão) até 262143</td>\n<td>Comprimento deve ser especificado préviamente (Fixo)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>STRING</td>\n<td>Cadeia de caracteres</td>\n<td>Váriavel (<a href=\"https://help.sap.com/doc/abapdocu_751_index_htm/7.51/en-us/abenmemory_consumption_2.htm\">Max Size</a>)</td>\n<td>Comprimento dinâmico</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_char           <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">c</span>       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ABC123'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">LENGTH</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" Se o comprimento não for especificado, assume o padrão</span>\n    v_number_char    <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> n       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'123456'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">LENGTH</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_string         <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> string  <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Hello World!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_char2<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>        <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">c</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ABC123'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" Outra forma de especificar o comprimento (LENGTH)</span>\n    v_number_char2<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> n <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'123456'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<BR/>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"Tipos-Data-x2F-Hora\"><a href=\"#Tipos-Data-x2F-Hora\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tipos Data&#x2F;Hora\"></a>Tipos Data&#x2F;Hora</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Identificador</th>\n<th>Descrição</th>\n<th>Comprimento</th>\n<th>Formato</th>\n<th>Restrições</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>D</td>\n<td>Caracteres numéricos no formato de data</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>YYYYMMDD</td>\n<td>Ano (0001-9999), Mês (01-12), Dia (1-31)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>T</td>\n<td>Caracteres numéricos no formato de hora</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>HHMMSS</td>\n<td>Hora (00-23), Min (00-59), Seg (00-59)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_data <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> d <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">20221022</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>    <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" YYYYMMDD -> 22-10-2022</span>\n    v_hora <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> t <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">213200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>      <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" HHMMSS   -> 21:32:00</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<BR/>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"Tipos-Byte\"><a href=\"#Tipos-Byte\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tipos Byte\"></a>Tipos Byte</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Identificador</th>\n<th>Descrição</th>\n<th>Comprimento</th>\n<th>Detalhes</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>X</td>\n<td>Bytes &#x2F; Hexadecimais</td>\n<td>Byte (1 até 524287) Hex (00 até FF)</td>\n<td>Comprimento deve ser especificado préviamente (Fixo)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>XSTRING</td>\n<td>Cadeia de bytes &#x2F; hexadecimais</td>\n<td>Váriavel (<a href=\"https://help.sap.com/doc/abapdocu_751_index_htm/7.51/en-us/abenmemory_consumption_2.htm\">Max Size</a>)</td>\n<td>Comprimento dinâmico</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_xstring <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> xstring <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'20C4DD6DD965AF'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_hex<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">x</span>       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'FF'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>","feature":true,"text":"Os tipos de dados locais representam tipos de dados primitivos predefinidos para utilização em programas ABAP. Esses tipos possuem apenas at...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"ABAP","slug":"ABAP","count":3,"path":"api/categories/ABAP.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Curso ABAP","slug":"Curso-ABAP","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Curso-ABAP.json"},{"name":"Introdução ao ABAP","slug":"Introducao-ao-ABAP","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Introducao-ao-ABAP.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-li